    <h1>
      <span data-lang="fr">Le web,<br>vu depuis <em>l'Afrique</em></span>
      <span data-lang="en">The web,<br>seen from <em>Africa</em></span>
      <span data-lang="ar">الإنترنت،<br>كما يُرى من <em>أفريقيا</em></span>
      <span data-lang="moore">Web n,<br><em>Afrika</em> pʋgẽ yĩnga</span>
      <span data-lang="dioula">Ɛntɛrinɛti,<br><em>Afrika</em> fɛ ka tɛmɛ</span>
      <span data-lang="fulfulde">Enternet ngon,<br>janngo e <em>Afrik</em></span>
      <span data-lang="songhay">Enternet ga,<br>ye <em>Afrik</em> ra</span>
      <span data-lang="gourma">Enternet,<br>yi <em>Afrik</em> faŋu</span>
      <span data-lang="bm">Ɛntɛrinɛti,<br><em>Afrika</em> la ka tɛmɛ</span>
      <span data-lang="ha">Intanet,<br>daga <em>Afirka</em></span>
      <span data-lang="wo">Enternet bi,<br>te ci <em>Àfrig</em> la</span>
      <span data-lang="sw">Mtandao,<br>ukionekana kutoka <em>Afrika</em></span>
      <span data-lang="yo">Íntánẹ́ẹ̀tì,<br>bí a ṣe ń wo láti <em>Áfíríkà</em></span>
      <span data-lang="am">ድር፣<br>ከ<em>አፍሪካ</em> ሲታይ</span>
      <span data-lang="om">Intarneetii,<br><em>Afrikaa</em> irraa argame</span>
      <span data-lang="ig">Ịntanetị,<br>ọ dị ka a hụrụ ya site na <em>Afrịka</em></span>
      <span data-lang="so">Internetka,<br>sida laga arkay <em>Afrika</em></span>
      <span data-lang="mg">Ny internet,<br>hita avy any <em>Afrika</em></span>
      <span data-lang="zu">I-web,<br>ibonakala kusuka <em>e-Afrika</em></span>
    </h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
      <span data-lang="fr">DUNIA Browser est un navigateur de bureau pensé pour les utilisateurs africains — rapide, respectueux de la vie privée, et centré sur les contenus du continent.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">DUNIA Browser is a desktop browser built for African users — fast, privacy-focused, and centered on local content.</span>
      <span data-lang="ar">DUNIA Browser متصفح مكتبي مصمم للمستخدمين الأفارقة — سريع، يحترم خصوصيتك، ومتمحور حول محتوى القارة.</span>
      <span data-lang="moore">DUNIA Browser yaa ordinatɛɛr navigatɛɛr ning b tũnda Afiriki neba yĩnga — zodgo, tɩ y pãnd tiig sɩd, la b kõ Afiriki yɩɩla.</span>
      <span data-lang="dioula">DUNIA Browser ye ordinatɛri dɔnnibaga do ye min kɛra Afrika mɔgɔw bolo — joona, i ka gundo lakana, ani Afrika kunnafoni ma jɛ.</span>
      <span data-lang="fulfulde">DUNIA Browser ko navigateer ordinateer danyaaɗo ngam jeyaaɓe Afrik — jaɓɓungel, suɓaali fawaango, kadi ɗemɗe adunanke.</span>
      <span data-lang="songhay">DUNIA Browser ga navigateer ga ban Afrik maye — ciiri, n d'a ga nda ay ga, kala Afrik ganda.</span>
      <span data-lang="gourma">DUNIA Browser na navigateur nawubu ma Afrik ŋubi yiŋ — bɛli, bu yiŋ yaafu, kali Afrik ŋa.</span>
      <span data-lang="bm">DUNIA Browser ye ordinatɛri dɔnnibaga ye min daɲɛra Afrika mɔgɔw bolo — joona, i ka gundo lakana, ani Afrika kunnafoni ma.</span>
      <span data-lang="ha">DUNIA Browser na'ura ce ta binciken intanet da aka tsara don masu amfani na Afirka — da sauri, tana kare sirri, kuma tana mai da hankali kan abubuwan nahiyar.</span>
      <span data-lang="wo">DUNIA Browser moromoro ordinateer la bu sos ngir jëfandikukat yi Àfrig — jagañ, bu xalaat siri sa mbir, te toppatoo xam-xam yi Àfrig.</span>
      <span data-lang="sw">DUNIA Browser ni kivinjari cha kompyuta kilichoundwa kwa watumiaji wa Afrika — cha haraka, kinachoheshimu faragha yako, na kinachozingatia maudhui ya bara.</span>
      <span data-lang="yo">DUNIA Browser jẹ́ aṣàwákiri kọ̀mpútà tí a ṣe fún àwọn olùmúlò Áfíríkà — yára, tí ń bọ̀wọ̀ fún ìkọ̀kọ̀ rẹ, tí ó sì ń dojú kọ àwọn àkóónú kọ́ńtínẹ́ǹtì.</span>
      <span data-lang="am">DUNIA Browser ለአፍሪካ ተጠቃሚዎች የተሰራ የዴስክቶፕ አሳሽ ነው — ፈጣን፣ ለግላዊነትህ አክባሪ፣ እና የአህጉሪቱን ይዘቶች ያማከለ።</span>
      <span data-lang="om">DUNIA Browser browserri kompiyuutaraa fayyadamtoota Afrikaaf uumame — ariifataa, iccitii kee kabaja, galmee Afrikaas of keessaa qaba.</span>
      <span data-lang="ig">DUNIA Browser bụ ihe ọchịchọ komputa emere maka ndị ọrụ Afrịka — ngwa ọsọ, na-elekọta nzuzo gị, ma lekwasị anya n'ihe ọ bụla nke ọhịa.</span>
      <span data-lang="so">DUNIA Browser waa browser kombiyuutar loo sameeyay isticmaalayaasha Afrika — degdeg ah, xushmeeya xogta gaarka ah, una xushmeeya waxyaabaha qaaradda.</span>
      <span data-lang="mg">DUNIA Browser dia navigateur solosaina natao ho an'ny mpampiasa Afrikanina — haingana, manaja ny tsiambaratelo, ary mifantoka amin'ny votoatin'ny kaontinanta.</span>
      <span data-lang="zu">I-DUNIA Browser iyibrowser yekhompyutha eyakhiwa kubasebenzisi base-Afrika — isheshayo, ihlonipha imfihlelo yakho, futhi igxile emqukambini we-Afrika.</span>
    </p>

    <div class="badges">
      <div class="badge"><span>🛡️</span>
